data.title: President Harry S. Truman greeting King Faisal II of Iraq
data.meta_description: Harry S. Truman, President of the United States, receives His Majesty King Faisal II Al-Hashimi of Iraq at the White House. From photograph album, "Visit of his Majesty the King of Iraq and his Royal Highness the Regent of Iraq to the United States of America, August 12 to September 8, 1952."
